{"seq": 9, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-22T17:36:00+00:00", "type": "cache_warning", "data": {"provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "approx_prefix_tokens": 2154, "min_cacheable": 4096, "note": "前綴低於門檻，快取會靜默失效（不會多收錢，只是沒有效益）。"}}
{"seq": 10, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-22T17:36:02+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:chen_yuan:act", "tier": "dialogue", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3306, "out": 170, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "才六點，林淑就醒了啊。她昨天值夜班，不知道累不累。", "action": {"kind": "speak", "target_area": "", "target_agent": "林淑", "utterance": "怎麼這麼早起來？不多睡會兒嗎？", "object": ""}, "plan": "先跟林淑講幾句話，然後去咖啡館買早餐。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 11, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-22T17:36:04+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:guo_bo:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3393, "out": 156, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "凌晨四點半天還黑著就起床，這把老骨頭真是越來越硬了。陳原那小子應該快起床準備上班了吧，得先把今天的報紙擺好。", "action": {"kind": "interact", "target_area": "", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": "整理報攤，把今天的日報夾上鐵絲，順手把那一盒難吃的橘子糖往內挪了挪"}, "plan": "整理好攤位後就坐在椅子上等第一批客人，大概是陳原或王浩會經過吧。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 12, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-22T17:36:04+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:mei_yi:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3381, "out": 203, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "這時間還早，先準備咖啡機，把今天的狀態調好。陳原差不多再過一陣子就會走過來了。", "action": {"kind": "interact", "target_area": "", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": "打開咖啡機開關，檢查濾紙和咖啡豆，準備迎接第一批客人"}, "plan": "先整理店面，等陳原過來，再看看要聊什麼話題。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 13, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-22T17:36:04+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:lin_shu:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3429, "out": 294, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "他又要去保險行了，這日子一天天過得真快。我得先弄點吃的，演好這個「妻子」的角色。", "action": {"kind": "interact", "target_area": "", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": "走進廚房給陳原倒一杯水"}, "plan": "稍微問候一下他，準備早餐，確認他今天的精神狀態。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 14, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-22T17:36:04+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:wang_hao:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3406, "out": 318, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "太早了，這鬼地方早上六點根本沒人會來。先整理一下桌子，等陳原過來一起去喝杯咖啡好了。", "action": {"kind": "interact", "target_area": "", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": "把桌上的文件疊整齊"}, "plan": "在保險行待著，等陳原出現，然後約他去梅姨那喝咖啡。"}, "error": null}}
{"seq": 15, "tick": 0, "wall": "2026-07-22T17:36:04+00:00", "type": "llm_call", "data": {"key": "0:su_qing:act", "tier": "routine", "provider": "gemini", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "usage": {"inp": 3404, "out": 352, "c_write": 0, "c_read": 0}, "output": {"thought": "早上的圖書館冷得要命，空氣裡全是灰塵的味道。既然接了這份工作，還是得把架上的東西整理一下，至少看起來要像個認真的館員。", "action": {"kind": "interact", "target_area": "", "target_agent": "", "utterance": "", "object": "整理書架上的舊報紙合訂本，順便拍掉封面上的灰塵"}, "plan": "先整理好館內環境，等接近陳原上班的時間，再找機會看能不能在門口遇到他。"}, "error": null}}
